### Envato Tuts+ Tutorial: Creating a News Reader App with React Native

#### Instructor: Wernher-Bel Ancheta

In this tutorial I'll be showing you how to create a Hacker News Reader using React Native. We'll be using the ListView component to render a list of news items and the WebView to render the web page for reading the news.

Source files for the Envato Tuts+ tutorial: [Creating a News Reader App with React Native]()

**Read this tutorial on [Envato Tuts+](https://code.tutsplus.com)**.